name: Katsushika Hokusai (Fate Grand Order)
description:
Lora model for Katsushika Hokusai from Fate Grand Order. All preview images were done with weight 0.8.

Most of art for this character is so elaborate that I was half expecting I'm gonna end with something completely random. But it works, even if clothes details are not exactly as they should be (if there even is an established version anyway).

Few cool prompts you can use:

  • First ascension - katsushika hokusai \(fate\), kimono, obi, hair flower, sandals, tabi, hair stick, fur collar

  • Second ascension - katsushika hokusai \(fate\), kimono, hair flower, sandals, tabi, hair stick, off shoulder, yellow bow

  • Third ascension - katsushika hokusai \(fate\), hair ornament, black dress, pale skin, tentacles, red eyes

  • Casual outfit - katsushika hokusai \(fate\), single hair bun, hooded jacket, shoulder bag, hairpin, skirt, shoes

  • Bikini - katsushika hokusai \(fate\), white bikini, goggles, sash, floral print, bracelet, thigh strap, belt, hair flower, sidelocks, sandals

Tips and tricks:

  • tokitarou \(fate\), octopus works! :')

  • You can replace black dress for highleg in third ascension version for some cool design I've seen on some artworks.

  • Many artworks have her holding paintbrush so you can add holding, paintbrush into negative.

Also recently I feel like this website have been marking pictures 18+ at random.
